narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Commonsense Housing INC is a Community/Behavioral Health provider based in Eddington, ME. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $22.2M in Medicaid payments across 22K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $22.2M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
